                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-61-off390 t18210214-61-cd394"></join>, I sent him to Mr. Lance, to receive 1 l., the balance of an account; he returned, and said it was not convenient for him to pay it. Nine days after I discharged him, but afterwards had him apprehended. He gave an account of the money received on my account, which I found correct. He never accounted to me for this money.</p>
